    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: This is a &quot;Support the Devs Pack + Original Soundtrack&quot; for Familiar Friends. This DLC does not affect in-game content.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you so much for choosing to support us in our journey while rocking out to tasty jams! It really means the world to us and we appreciate you more than words can express! ♥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras/f4594b19d6b862cc323f55d225876771.avif?t=1763680777\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras_big/f4594b19d6b862cc323f55d225876771.avif?t=1763680777 width=800 height=532 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to A Beautiful Collection of Darkness: Volume 3 - Familiar Friends!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is the 3rd Volume in our new series - <u>A Beautiful Collection of Darkness</u>. You can find our other volumes on Steam!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In this Supporter Pack / OST + Art Pack, explore an upbeat, yet relaxing musical experience sure to get your head and heart moving! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras/fd8e20e11d7ff68910ba9cdadcc60c11.avif?t=1763680777\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras_big/fd8e20e11d7ff68910ba9cdadcc60c11.avif?t=1763680777 width=800 height=532 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Featured in Volume 3 are all songs from </strong><strong><u>Familiar Friends</u></strong><strong>!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We've also included over a dozen pictures of original art found in the game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Music Files come in standard MP3 format with optional download of WAV.)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special thanks to </strong><strong><u>Randumb Studios</u></strong><strong> &amp; <u>&quot;A Beautiful Collection of Darkness&quot;</u>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Joshua Benson, Amy Nguyen, Samantha Reed, Sven Brännström, Billy &quot;The Brain&quot; Bozeman, Erica Chavez, and Shamus O'Reiley.)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras/6e7f9847cf0fdc3ac10c4751325bf57d.avif?t=1763680777\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292850/extras_big/6e7f9847cf0fdc3ac10c4751325bf57d.avif?t=1763680777 width=800 height=532 /></span></p>",
